OL,6,FA police detective who had sex with a
OL,7,Fwoman who had reported being sexually
OL,8,Fassaulted has been found guilty of
OL,9,Fabusing his position.
OL,11,FFormer Det Con Wasim Bashir, 55, was
OL,12,Fworking for West Yorkshire Police when
OL,13,Fhe became involved with the victim.
OL,15,FHe was investigated by the Independent
OL,16,FOffice for Police Conduct's (IOPC)
OL,17,Fanti-corruption unit, after a woman
OL,18,Fcame forward.
