OL,6,FEvidence gathered during the
OL,7,Finvestigation showed Bashir, who
OL,8,Fretired from the force in June,
OL,9,Fcontacted a woman who had reported
OL,10,Fserious sexual offences and domestic
OL,11,Fabuse without any identified policing
OL,12,Fpurpose. He then began a sexual
OL,13,Frelationship with her.
OL,15,FThe officer, who had been a specialist
OL,16,Frape investigator, was convicted of
OL,17,Fmisconduct in a public office but
OL,18,Fcleared of a second offence on the
OL,19,Fdirections of a judge at Sheffield
OL,20,FCrown Court.
