OL,6,FHe was remanded in custody and will be
OL,7,Fsentenced on 29 August.
OL,9,FIOPC Director Emily Barry said: "As a
OL,10,Fpolice officer, DC Bashir held
OL,11,Fsignificant power so to abuse his
OL,12,Fposition for a sexual purpose was an
OL,13,Finvidious and corrupt use of that
OL,14,Fpower.
