OL,4,Cvictim guilty of abusing position
OL,6,F"Despite being an officer with 28
OL,7,Fyears' service, Bashir blatantly
OL,8,Fdisregarded the rules designed to
OL,9,Fprotect the public and maintain
OL,10,Fconfidence in the police. His actions
OL,11,Fcan only have undermined trust in
OL,12,Fpolicing."
OL,14,FThe investigation found evidence
OL,15,FBashir engaged in sexual activity,
OL,16,Fincluding intercourse, with one woman
OL,17,Fon three separate occasions while he
OL,18,Fwas part of the team investigating a
OL,19,Fsexual offence which she had reported
OL,20,Fto the police.
