OL,6,FEvidence was also found that Bashir
OL,7,Fhad posted photographs of himself and
OL,8,Fthe woman online, presenting them as a
OL,9,Fcouple, without her consent.
OL,11,FDet Supt Natalie Dawson, deputy head
OL,12,Fof West Yorkshire Police's
OL,13,FProfessional Standards Directorate,
OL,14,Fsaid: "For a police officer to pursue
OL,15,Fa sexual relationship with a
OL,16,Fvulnerable woman who had come forward
OL,17,Fto report being victim of a sexual
OL,18,Foffence is nothing short of abhorrent.
OL,26,@vD@GOU
